### 星际漂流计划 API 测试
### 使用 VS Code 的 REST Client 插件运行这些测试
### 或者复制到 Postman/Insomnia 中使用

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@contentType = application/json

### ============================================
### 1. 用户认证测试
### ============================================

### 1.1 注册新用户
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "test_user_001",
  "email": "test001@example.com",
  "password": "Test123456"
}

### 1.2 注册第二个用户（用于测试）
# @name register2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "test_user_002",
  "email": "test002@example.com",
  "password": "Test123456"
}

### 1.3 登录用户
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test001@example.com",
  "password": "Test123456"
}

### 1.4 获取当前用户信息
# @name me
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

### 1.5 刷新 Token
# @name refresh
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{login.response.body.tokens.refreshToken}}"
}

### 1.6 测试错误：邮箱已存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "duplicate_user",
  "email": "test001@example.com",
  "password": "Test123456"
}

### 1.7 测试错误：用户名已存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "test_user_001",
  "email": "another@example.com",
  "password": "Test123456"
}

### 1.8 测试错误：密码错误
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test001@example.com",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 1.9 测试错误：用户不存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "nonexistent@example.com",
  "password": "Test123456"
}

### ============================================
### 2. 生物创建测试
### ============================================

### 2.1 创建生物（需要登录）
# @name createCreature
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

{
  "imageData": "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==",
  "userCustomization": {
    "name": "测试生物001",
    "story": "这是一个测试生物的故事"
  }
}

### 2.2 创建第二个生物
# @name createCreature2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

{
  "imageData": "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mP8z8DwHwAFBQIAX8jx0gAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==",
  "userCustomization": {
    "name": "星云漂流者",
    "story": "来自遥远星云的神秘生物"
  }
}

### 2.3 测试错误：未登录创建生物
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "imageData": "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==",
  "userCustomization": {
    "name": "未授权生物"
  }
}

### 2.4 测试错误：缺少图片数据
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

{
  "userCustomization": {
    "name": "无图片生物"
  }
}

### ============================================
### 3. 生物查询测试（公开接口，无需登录）
### ============================================

### 3.1 获取所有生物（分页）
# @name getAllCreatures
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures?page=1&limit=10

### 3.2 获取所有生物（第二页）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures?page=2&limit=5

### 3.3 获取单个生物详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{createCreature.response.body.id}}

### 3.4 随机遇见生物
# @name randomCreature
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/random

### 3.5 测试错误：生物不存在
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### ============================================
### 4. 我的生物测试（需要登录）
### ============================================

### 4.1 获取我创建的生物列表
# @name myCreatures
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/my/list
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

### 4.2 测试错误：未登录获取我的生物
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/my/list

### ============================================
### 5. 生物更新测试（需要登录且是创建者）
### ============================================

### 5.1 更新生物信息
# @name updateCreature
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{createCreature.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

{
  "name": "测试生物001（已更新）",
  "backstory": "这是更新后的背景故事，更加详细和有趣"
}

### 5.2 只更新名称
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{createCreature.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

{
  "name": "新名称"
}

### 5.3 只更新背景故事
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{createCreature.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

{
  "backstory": "全新的背景故事"
}

### 5.4 测试错误：未登录更新
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{createCreature.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "未授权更新"
}

### 5.5 测试错误：更新他人的生物（使用第二个用户的token）
# 先登录第二个用户
# @name login2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test002@example.com",
  "password": "Test123456"
}

###
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{createCreature.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login2.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

{
  "name": "尝试修改他人生物"
}

### ============================================
### 6. 生物删除测试（需要登录且是创建者）
### ============================================

### 6.1 创建一个用于删除的生物
# @name creatureToDelete
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

{
  "imageData": "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==",
  "userCustomization": {
    "name": "待删除生物"
  }
}

### 6.2 删除生物
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{creatureToDelete.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

### 6.3 验证删除（应该返回404）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{creatureToDelete.response.body.id}}

### 6.4 测试错误：未登录删除
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{createCreature.response.body.id}}

### 6.5 测试错误：删除他人的生物
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{createCreature.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login2.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

### ============================================
### 7. 综合测试场景
### ============================================

### 7.1 完整用户流程测试
# 1. 注册新用户
# @name flowUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "flow_test_user",
  "email": "flow@example.com",
  "password": "Flow123456"
}

### 2. 登录
# @name flowLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "flow@example.com",
  "password": "Flow123456"
}

### 3. 创建生物
# @name flowCreature
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{flowLogin.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

{
  "imageData": "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==",
  "userCustomization": {
    "name": "流程测试生物",
    "story": "这是一个完整流程测试"
  }
}

### 4. 查看我的生物
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/my/list
Authorization: Bearer {{flowLogin.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

### 5. 更新生物
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{flowCreature.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{flowLogin.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

{
  "name": "流程测试生物（已更新）"
}

### 6. 查看更新后的生物
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{flowCreature.response.body.id}}

### 7. 浏览所有生物
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures?page=1&limit=20

### 8. 随机遇见
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/random

### ============================================
### 8. 边界测试
### ============================================

### 8.1 测试超长用户名
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "this_is_a_very_long_username_that_exceeds_the_maximum_length_allowed",
  "email": "longname@example.com",
  "password": "Test123456"
}

### 8.2 测试无效邮箱格式
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "invalid_email_user",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "password": "Test123456"
}

### 8.3 测试弱密码
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "weak_password_user",
  "email": "weak@example.com",
  "password": "123"
}

### 8.4 测试超大分页参数
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures?page=999999&limit=1000

### 8.5 测试负数分页参数
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures?page=-1&limit=-10

### ============================================
### 测试完成
### ============================================

### 清理测试数据（可选）
### 注意：这会删除测试过程中创建的生物
### 取消注释以下代码来执行清理

# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{createCreature.response.body.id}}
# Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{createCreature2.response.body.id}}
# Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}

# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/creatures/{{flowCreature.response.body.id}}
# Authorization: Bearer {{flowLogin.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}
